    "DQL represents a fundamental advancement in the field, opening doors to more sophisticated and capable AI systems that can learn directly from raw sensory inputs and navigate complex decision-making scenarios.",
    "A novel application of DQL in traffic management aims to significantly reduce congestion by optimizing traffic signal timings.",
    "This approach leverages the DQL algorithm's ability to learn and adapt to complex, dynamic environments.",
    "By integrating real-time traffic data, such as vehicle flow and occupancy sensors, the DQL model can predict and respond to traffic patterns with high precision.",
    "The model continuously updates its strategy based on traffic conditions, proactively adjusting signal timings to minimize jams and improve overall traffic flow."
